{
  "stem": "12666.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to read the document.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And attached to it, a so-called analysis sheet, to describe, in English, what the document is all about, particularly the highlights.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had to sign the analysis sheet, attach to the document, and give it to the lawyer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the lawyer would read our sheet of paper and then decide which part of the document should be introduced as evidence in court, and then send it to the translating division to have a certified translation.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Sometimes we had to do some interpreting, like I did interrupting on the Krupp trial, which was stopped, and Krupp went back to business.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was one trial that was stopped in the middle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I was working on the main trial against the Nazi government.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I saw all those members of the Nazi government.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one man that did impress me was Goering.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Goering was quite deflated, but he is the only one who had the guts to recognize his crimes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He talked for two days in his defense, and he said that, if I had to start it all over again, I would do the same thing because I did it for the greatness of my people.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of the other were saying, well, we followed the orders of our Fuhrer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have our will, so we are innocent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, in fact, Ribbentrop went even so far when he was asked, did you drive a certain road in Berlin to work?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He says, yes, I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you [INAUDIBLE] that concentration camp that was outskirts of Berlin?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, no, that's not a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a home for retired Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ribbentrop was saying, anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it's interesting how three people were acquitted.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
